## Mapeo rápido: función → archivo saga

| Función `api/index.js` | Saga principal |
|--------------------------|----------------|
| `postLogin` | `userSaga` |
| `getLocalities` | `genericsSaga` |
| `postMother`, `getMother`, `getMotherId`, `putMother`, `getStatisticsLocalities`, `getStatisticsAgeMother` | `motherSaga` |
| `postVolunteer`, `putVolunteer`, `getVolunteers`, `getVolunteersFree`, `getVolunteersStates`, `getVolunteerById`, `postAssistance`, `getAssistance` | `volunteerSaga` |
| `postBaby`, `getBabys`, `getBabysFree` | `babySaga` |
| `postAssignmentGenerate`, `postDetailAssignment`, `postStartHug`, `postEndHug`, `getAssignmentToday`, `getAssignmentTodayById`, `getStatisticsAssignmentMonth` | `assignmentSaga` |
| `getSupplies`, `getStatisticsSupplies` | `supplySaga` |

